{"tid":113044,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[屋村撚]屋企好撚多跳蝨，求救！","createTime":"2017-02-08T15:30:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T14:58:07.000Z","uid":27539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9faf3b98b5cb8137d72c7ebad2d1a5dd648f52c","tid":113044,"uid":27539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:30:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">屋企有一貓一狗，近排天氣太潮濕，屋企突然間好撚多蝨，加上隻貓成日出去玩野左好多蝨返黎，試過同佢沖完涼幾日之後都係無好過，有滴蝨藥，帶蝨帶，沖涼用殺蝨沖涼液，情況好左少少但夜晚訓教比d仆街蝨係咁咬尻我同屋企人，飲飲下水都可以有隻蝨係隻杯到，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可以點搞？隻貓個個禮拜都沖涼又對隻貓唔好，我隻狗平時少出街加上短毛會好少少，十日沖一次都得，問題係隻貓度，唔知係咪因為老貓所以抵抗力弱左係咁野到D蝨返黎，以前都未試過咁嚴重，每個星期沖一次涼對貓有無害？想買煙霧果D炸下間屋，邊一隻好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 百佳賣果d有無用？求一樣都係住屋村既巴絲教下我有咩方法可以改善到？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"2881c2afd3aaf39cb005f968d818763305dc4418","tid":113044,"uid":27539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/08/233751_8b7fc5682d0eba48771180dbb7bb59bc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F08%2F233751_8b7fc5682d0eba48771180dbb7bb59bc.jpg&h=d6d01406&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VNxH77E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVNxH77E.jpg&h=22d35e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n養左好耐兩隻老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 都係領養返黎，勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2091a2c5fc97a69668698b9ce7696479e6420f0","tid":113044,"uid":27539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:22:04.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1797e427e25537215c34e8fa3bd6d26850f7531b","tid":113044,"ui